Nagpunta si Pheem sa isang drug party!

00:34:24.600 --> 00:34:26.090
Tingnan mo akong mabuti.

00:34:28.199 --> 00:34:30.330
Mukha ba akong tanga sayo Chet?

00:34:30.840 --> 00:34:31.320
ha?

00:34:32.489 --> 00:34:35.760
Ikaw ang nasa likod ng insidente ng droga.

00:34:38.679 --> 00:34:42.130
Pinilit kong aminin si Pheem
at sinabihan silang itigil ang imbestigasyon

00:34:42.130 --> 00:34:44.400
dahil ikaw ang panganay kong anak!

00:34:44.570 --> 00:34:46.770
Ikaw ang mukha ng pamilyang Thanavej!

00:34:47.969 --> 00:34:49.719
Tingnan mo kung paano mo ako binayaran.

00:34:50.159 --> 00:34:51.580
Gumawa ka ng deal sa likod ko!

00:34:51.580 --> 00:34:52.560
At kinagat mo ang kamay na nagpapakain sa iyo!

00:34:52.560 --> 00:34:53.679
kawawa kang anak!

00:34:56.260 --> 00:34:56.929
Tatay.

00:34:57.060 --> 00:34:58.170
I'm sorry, Dad.

00:34:58.400 --> 00:34:59.650
Hindi ko na uulitin.

00:35:07.360 --> 00:35:10.850
Humanap ka ng bagong pondo
para sa proyekto ng health center.

00:35:11.810 --> 00:35:14.060
Kung hindi, tatawagan ko si Pheem.

00:35:31.470 --> 00:35:34.360
[Ospital ng Thanavej]

00:35:34.360 --> 00:35:35.360
Darn it!

00:35:36.490 --> 00:35:38.580
Bakit kailangan niyang mamatay ngayon?

00:35:39.200 --> 00:35:41.260
Ang aming buong plano ay ganap na nasira!

00:35:42.890 --> 00:35:44.800
Aalamin ko kung sino ang may gawa nito.

00:35:44.800 --> 00:35:46.460
Sino pa kaya kung hindi si Pheem?

00:35:46.570 --> 00:35:48.370
Yung bastos na Phem!

00:35:49.340 --> 00:35:51.200
I wonder kung saan siya nagtatago!

00:35:52.490 --> 00:35:54.090
Hindi ko na siya hahayaang bumalik.

00:35:54.570 --> 00:35:55.780
Hindi kailanman.

00:35:56.290 --> 00:35:57.400
Papatayin ko siya!

00:36:08.680 --> 00:36:10.130
Tumatawag si Wut, Mr. Chet.

00:36:14.420 --> 00:36:15.170
Ano ito?

00:36:15.700 --> 00:36:17.000
Diba sabi ko wag mo akong kontakin?

00:36:17.000 --> 00:36:20.160
Um... I... Narinig kong pinaalis si Pheem.

00:36:20.360 --> 00:36:22.160
Pwede ba akong bumalik ngayon?

